reviewText: Most of this is pretty common sense stuff, but there are a few things that are pertinent to pets that are very important.

I was hoping this video would be more detailed. Actually it is VERY basic. For those of us that have experience it is a waste. For those that do not know a thing about what to do if cat has object embedded in body, or how to properly splint, or treat a burn then fine it's good for you.
